name: Get Out Of The Dungeon (Nageswar)
description:
You entered a magical dungeon and you were trapped there as you are getting cloned and losing to your own self. Can you escape NOW....?

Controls :

Move : Left & Right Arrows

Jump : Up arrow

Double Jump : Up Arrow two times

Attack : Space

Face Left Side : L

Face Right Side : R

Get to the bottom right corner of the level to get into the next dungeon(level)...
